<dl id="n12150b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12150b">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12150b"> 150(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> council of Perpignan</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Et voici que les &eacute;v&eacute;nements qui l&apos;avaient tenu &eacute;loign&eacute; de l&apos;Espagne l&apos;y ram&egrave;nent en 1409, apr&egrave;s le concile de Perpignan. <br><font color="green">[And this is how the events that had made him stay away from Spain now brought him back in 1409, after the <mark>council of Perpignan</mark>.]</font> <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 234</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
